<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        .body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .header { background-color: #1e40af; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        
        .content { padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .status-badge { display: inline-block; background-color: #fff5f5; color: #c53030; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; border: 1px solid #feb2b2; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        
        .main-info { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #edf2f7; border-radius: 8px; width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .main-info th { background: #f7fafc; color: #718096; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 10px; border-bottom: 2px solid #edf2f7; }
        .main-info td { padding: 15px 10px; color: #2d3748; font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #edf2f7; }

        .comment-box { background: #fffaf0; border-left: 4px solid #ed8936; padding: 15px; text-align: left; margin: 0 5px; }
        .comment-box strong { color: #9c4221; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 13px; }
        .comment-text { color: #7b341e; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; }

        .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #a0aec0; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #edf2f7; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="body">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Metas Perú S.A.C</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">✖ HORA EXTRA NO APROBADA</div>
            <p style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 25px;">Estimado(a) colaborador(a), se ha revisado su marcación y no ha sido posible validar la hora extra.</p>
            
            <table class="main-info">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Tienda</th>
                        <th>Fecha</th>
                        <th>H. Extra</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="font-weight: bold; color: #1e40af;">{{tienda}}</td>
                        <td>{{fecha}}</td>
                        <td style="font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold;">{{hrx}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="comment-box">
                <strong>Motivo del rechazo:</strong>
                <span class="comment-text">"{{comentario}}"</span>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0; margin-top: 25px;">Responsable de revisión: {{usuario_responsable}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            Este es un correo informativo del Sistema de Gestión de Tiempos.<br>
            © 2026 Metas Perú S.A.C
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>